comments: Valanciunas (MEM) makes marginal contact to Collins' (ATL) side while rebounding.
Huerter (ATL) makes contact to Morant's (MEM) body on the drive that affects his SQBR.
Young (ATL) reaches back and grabs Allen's (MEM) jersey and affects his ability to defend on the drive to the basket.
Morant (MEM) makes marginal contact with Collins (ATL) on the perimeter and does not affect his FOM.
Collins (ATL) jumps vertical and makes marginal contact to his side and off arm as Morant (MEM) extends his left arm away from his body on the driving shot attempt.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bogdanovic (ATL) and absorbs the contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Reddish (ATL) and absorbs the contact.
Reddish (ATL) makes contact to the arm of Brooks (MEM) that affects his ability to follow through on the shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) cleanly dislodges the ball from Young (ATL).
Reddish (ATL) makes marginal contact to Allen's (MEM) body on his shot near the rim.
Morant (MEM) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (ATL).
Hunter (ATL) makes marginal contact to Morant's (MEM) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) extends his leg into Young's (ATL) path that trips him and affects his SQBR.
